sentences.sContent: By combining the Clockwork Decoy and a common electric light, you can illuminate even the tenebrous tunnels!
sentences.sContent_eng: By combining the Clockwork Decoy and a common electric light, you can illuminate even the tenebrous tunnels!
sentences.sCn: 只要将“发条诱饵装置”和一盏普通的“电灯”组合在一起，你甚至能让整条漆黑的隧道亮如白昼！
